data.title: ICP concert
data.text: All the staff was nice and worked quickly for the amount of people that where there. Bathrooms were kinda nasty but there were lots of drunk people. Would definitely go back

data.title: Good place to dance and have a drink
data.text: The bar has a pretty good DJ on the top floor with a dance area. Bars are on the 1st and 2nd floors with a good selection of beers and mixed drinks. Mostly undergrads in attendance, but relatively relaxed compared to the usual college bar.

data.title: Oh ouch
data.text: Went back after graduation for a friend's wedding - OUCH. This place has gotten awful. When it opened it had bathroom doors, clean toilets and drinks with alcohol. Now, it has no bathroom doors, toilets that may not flush and for sure an uneducated bartender staff. Yikes!!!!!!!  I'd rather stay at the Scum-It.

data.title: A Gem
data.text: The Blue Moose is truly a gem in the Iowa City area from its great atmosphere to the great shows that can be seen here!  It also offers a great drink selection and awesome service!  It is an absolute must checkout in the Iowa City area!

data.title: 24 tipi diversi di birra alla spina
data.text: Pub molto semplice in centro città, la cosa che colpisce di più è l'ampia scelta di birre alla spina (24 tipi diversi di cui alcune artigianali locali). Ne ho provate diverse e sono molto buone. Esistono anche i boccali giganti a forma di stivale da cowboy, un tocco di classe del midwest. Al piano di sopra karaoke e musica dal vivo su un piccolo palco.
